name: Trango Big Bro Tube Chock
description: Expanding spring-loaded tube chocks with lock-off screw collar is effective in offwidth cracks. Depress the button to allow the tube to expand to the width of a crack and then tighten the collar to lock the unit into place. Big Bros are relatively light, compact, and stable compared to spring-loaded camming devices.Offset ends allow for secure angled placement.Holes at one end of the tube need to be slung.Made of aluminum.
